==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Keystone State
<hw>Key"stone` State</hw>. <def>Pennsylvania; -- a nickname alluding to
its having been the central one of the 13 original United States, at the
time of formation of the Constitution.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

